show.title: Pyaada Bana Wazir
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/UfZyaG
show.description: World-famous chess grandmaster MK mysteriously vanishes at the peak of his career—only to find his soul reborn in the body of a timid, orphaned boy tormented by his cruel relatives. As MK’s sharp intellect and fearless spirit begin to surface, the boy gains the strength to stand up for himself. Teaming up with a young fan from MK’s past, they uncover a sinister plot: MK was kidnapped and kept unconscious by a rival desperate to steal his place in the global chess arena. In a dramatic final showdown, MK regains his body, defeats his rival, and breaks the mystical bond—setting both himself and the boy free.
